{"tid":1119612,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"淺談power rangers，迪士尼同 Marvel 的關係","createTime":"2019-04-22T05:02:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T05:44:15.000Z","uid":238673,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"397e1f358df0aa9e032572dee30b9fdd81a6ca6d","tid":1119612,"uid":238673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T05:02:55.000Z","msg":"2001年，power rangers始創公司Saban賣版權比迪士尼，由Ninja Storm(忍風)到rpm(炎神)呢幾套都由迪士尼接手拍power ramgers, 雖然依然強調低成本，但依然拍出同saban完全不同的風格，剪日版片段幾乎只有巨大戰，等身戰幾乎沒有用日版片，而美版這時期打鬥質素奇高，saban時期也只有初代及某幾部打鬥比較突出，而作為當時saban最終作十週年wild force(百獸)班底已經是迪士尼，大約很多人知道 forever red呢集經典吧，無論卡士劇情打鬥都是一流水準。<br />\n在這幾套迪士尼pr中較廣為人知除了風格打鬥精彩外，dino thunder(爆龍)中tommy回歸; operation overdrive(轟轟)十五週年特別篇 once a ranger，也是經典，二代黑戰士adam park回歸，打鬥依然保持水準。<br />\n08年marvel開始mcu, 大家都知marvel已經是迪士尼期下，估計mcu這些出色動作場面也許是歸功於這段時間的power rangers吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有興趣的朋友可去找找上述集數一看<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee6d76b455f4404a3f64b23cce399d55847f00d","tid":1119612,"uid":238673,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T05:05:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NVTD6saxaA0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNVTD6saxaA0&d=1KnBewcMxCifpJVTRQbR6tLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=30d6ef44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NVTD6saxaA0</a><br />\n順手放上 once a ranger 其中一段精彩打鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b632605dcc0d5b0e88219b277e730b87fcb218","tid":1119612,"uid":34123,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T05:08:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541e87535af590ef2cc51278d42c8e08a00dfa34","tid":111961